metadata.name: Homeless Degen Alpha Collective
metadata.description: Homeless Degen Alpha Group(HDAG) is a community service based alpha group, who aim to help people without basic needs, and to spread the good word about good profitable plays. Our founder Died...We Became Homeless Degens...Then we got our shit together to start helping people IRL. #69ethOrNothing *any item listed for less than 69eth is held by someone who doesn't share our core beliefs or mission to help someone other than themselves. Please don't pay them ethereum. thank you
